{"tid":2301804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國大選] 最新計票：拜登得票數逾億，兩大候選人不史勢破歷史紀錄","createTime":"2020-11-26T14:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T19:01:14.000Z","uid":52658,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1dcc7a049828f1c49503e8f04b41cad07e1a71e7","tid":2301804,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3oWzYiP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3oWzYiP.png&h=629e028d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拜登：81,000,000<br />\n川普：74,000,000<br />\n<br />\n最新戰況：<br />\n全美46州份大局已定<br />\n只有賓州 威斯康辛 亞利桑納同喬治亞州4州存在暗湧<br />\n拜登選舉人票最少有249票<br />\n川普必須要在賓州翻盤 否則勢必敗選<br />\n<br />\n是日選戰懶人包<br />\n<br />\n賓州：<br />\n今早完成聽證會 法庭偏向認同選舉存在舞弊<br />\n下令撤回拜登該州勝選宣布<br />\n<br />\n亞利桑納州：<br />\n今早發現有約6000票誤計拜登帳下<br />\n拜登現存優勢不足5000票<br />\n<br />\n喬治亞州：<br />\n第三度驗票進行中<br />\n有待最終結果<br />\n<br />\n威斯康辛州：<br />\n川普團隊正申請上訴<br />\n暫未有最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">我川威武 川皇必勝<br />\n光復賓州 時代革命<br />\n賓亞威喬 缺一不可<br />\n川普連任 唯一出路</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c1ea6c981b2bacfebb4f92bf86dc5756816ae1","tid":2301804,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:49:55.000Z","msg":"標題打錯：<br />\n兩大候選人得票勢破歷史紀錄"},{"pid":"9e06808956071d330db621a6c7a1067d090c64ec","tid":2301804,"uid":69157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"21c1ea6c981b2bacfebb4f92bf86dc5756816ae1","tid":2301804,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:49:55.000Z","msg":"標題打錯：<br />\n兩大候選人得票勢破歷史紀錄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade8da0221ee3a520b8d0c69977e02da829dc6d6","tid":2301804,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"賓